{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I got my start"},{"time":3000,"text":"in writing and research"},{"time":5000,"text":"as a surgical trainee,"},{"time":8000,"text":"as someone who was a long ways away"},{"time":10000,"text":"from becoming any kind of an expert at anything."},{"time":13000,"text":"So the natural question you ask then at that point"},{"time":16000,"text":"is, how do I get good at what I'm trying to do?"},{"time":18000,"text":"And it became a question of,"},{"time":20000,"text":"how do we all get good"},{"time":22000,"text":"at what we're trying to do?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":25000,"text":"It's hard enough to learn to get the skills,"},{"time":29000,"text":"try to learn all the material you have to absorb"},{"time":32000,"text":"at any task you're taking on."},{"time":34000,"text":"I had to think about how I sew and how I cut,"},{"time":37000,"text":"but then also how I pick the right person"},{"time":39000,"text":"to come to an operating room."},{"time":41000,"text":"And then in the midst of all this"},{"time":43000,"text":"came this new context"},{"time":45000,"text":"for thinking about what it meant to be good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47000,"text":"In the last few years"},{"time":49000,"text":"we realized we were in the deepest crisis"},{"time":52000,"text":"of medicine's existence"},{"time":54000,"text":"due to something you don't normally think about"},{"time":56000,"text":"when you're a doctor"},{"time":58000,"text":"concerned with how you do good for people,"},{"time":61000,"text":"which is the cost"},{"time":63000,"text":"of health care."},{"time":65000,"text":"There's not a country in the world"},{"time":68000,"text":"that now is not asking"},{"time":70000,"text":"whether we can afford what doctors do."},{"time":73000,"text":"The political fight that we've developed"},{"time":76000,"text":"has become one around"},{"time":78000,"text":"whether it's the government that's the problem"},{"time":81000,"text":"or is it insurance companies that are the problem."},{"time":86000,"text":"And the answer is yes and no;"},{"time":90000,"text":"it's deeper than all of that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92000,"text":"The cause of our troubles"},{"time":94000,"text":"is actually the complexity that science has given us."},{"time":97000,"text":"And in order to understand this,"},{"time":99000,"text":"I'm going to take you back a couple of generations."},{"time":103000,"text":"I want to take you back"},{"time":105000,"text":"to a time when Lewis Thomas was writing in his book, \"The Youngest Science.\""},{"time":108000,"text":"Lewis Thomas was a physician-writer,"},{"time":110000,"text":"one of my favorite writers."},{"time":112000,"text":"And he wrote this book to explain, among other things,"},{"time":115000,"text":"what it was like to be a medical intern"},{"time":118000,"text":"at the Boston City Hospital"},{"time":120000,"text":"in the pre-penicillin year"},{"time":122000,"text":"of 1937."},{"time":125000,"text":"It was a time when medicine was cheap"},{"time":129000,"text":"and very ineffective."},{"time":133000,"text":"If you were in a hospital, he said,"},{"time":136000,"text":"it was going to do you good"},{"time":139000,"text":"only because it offered you"},{"time":141000,"text":"some warmth, some food, shelter,"},{"time":145000,"text":"and maybe the caring attention"},{"time":147000,"text":"of a nurse."},{"time":149000,"text":"Doctors and medicine"},{"time":153000,"text":"made no difference at all."},{"time":155000,"text":"That didn't seem to prevent the doctors"},{"time":157000,"text":"from being frantically busy in their days,"},{"time":159000,"text":"as he explained."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161000,"text":"What they were trying to do"},{"time":163000,"text":"was figure out whether you might have one of the diagnoses"},{"time":166000,"text":"for which they could do something."},{"time":169000,"text":"And there were a few."},{"time":171000,"text":"You might have a lobar pneumonia, for example,"},{"time":174000,"text":"and they could give you an antiserum,"},{"time":176000,"text":"an injection of rabid antibodies"},{"time":180000,"text":"to the bacterium streptococcus,"},{"time":183000,"text":"if the intern sub-typed it correctly."},{"time":187000,"text":"If you had an acute congestive heart failure,"},{"time":190000,"text":"they could bleed a pint of blood from you"},{"time":193000,"text":"by opening up an arm vein,"},{"time":196000,"text":"giving you a crude leaf preparation of digitalis"},{"time":199000,"text":"and then giving you oxygen by tent."},{"time":204000,"text":"If you had early signs of paralysis"},{"time":206000,"text":"and you were really good at asking personal questions,"},{"time":209000,"text":"you might figure out"},{"time":211000,"text":"that this paralysis someone has is from syphilis,"},{"time":214000,"text":"in which case you could give this nice concoction"},{"time":217000,"text":"of mercury and arsenic --"},{"time":221000,"text":"as long as you didn't overdose them and kill them."},{"time":226000,"text":"Beyond these sorts of things,"},{"time":228000,"text":"a medical doctor didn't have a lot that they could do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":233000,"text":"This was when the core structure of medicine"},{"time":235000,"text":"was created --"},{"time":237000,"text":"what it meant to be good at what we did"},{"time":240000,"text":"and how we wanted to build medicine to be."},{"time":242000,"text":"It was at a time"},{"time":244000,"text":"when what was known you could know,"},{"time":246000,"text":"you could hold it all in your head, and you could do it all."},{"time":249000,"text":"If you had a prescription pad,"},{"time":251000,"text":"if you had a nurse,"},{"time":253000,"text":"if you had a hospital"},{"time":255000,"text":"that would give you a place to convalesce, maybe some basic tools,"},{"time":258000,"text":"you really could do it all."},{"time":260000,"text":"You set the fracture, you drew the blood,"},{"time":263000,"text":"you spun the blood,"},{"time":265000,"text":"looked at it under the microscope,"},{"time":267000,"text":"you plated the culture, you injected the antiserum."},{"time":270000,"text":"This was a life as a craftsman."}]},{"cues":[{"time":275000,"text":"As a result, we built it around"},{"time":278000,"text":"a culture and set of values"},{"time":280000,"text":"that said what you were good at"},{"time":283000,"text":"was being daring,"},{"time":285000,"text":"at being courageous,"},{"time":287000,"text":"at being independent and self-sufficient."},{"time":291000,"text":"Autonomy was our highest value."},{"time":297000,"text":"Go a couple generations forward"},{"time":299000,"text":"to where we are, though,"},{"time":301000,"text":"and it looks like a completely different world."},{"time":303000,"text":"We have now found treatments"},{"time":306000,"text":"for nearly all of the tens of thousands of conditions"},{"time":310000,"text":"that a human being can have."},{"time":312000,"text":"We can't cure it all."},{"time":314000,"text":"We can't guarantee that everybody will live a long and healthy life."},{"time":317000,"text":"But we can make it possible"},{"time":319000,"text":"for most."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322000,"text":"But what does it take?"},{"time":324000,"text":"Well, we've now discovered"},{"time":326000,"text":"4,000 medical and surgical procedures."},{"time":330000,"text":"We've discovered 6,000 drugs"},{"time":333000,"text":"that I'm now licensed to prescribe."},{"time":336000,"text":"And we're trying to deploy this capability,"},{"time":338000,"text":"town by town,"},{"time":340000,"text":"to every person alive --"},{"time":344000,"text":"in our own country,"},{"time":346000,"text":"let alone around the world."},{"time":348000,"text":"And we've reached the point where we've realized,"},{"time":351000,"text":"as doctors,"},{"time":353000,"text":"we can't know it all."},{"time":355000,"text":"We can't do it all"},{"time":358000,"text":"by ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360000,"text":"There was a study where they looked"},{"time":362000,"text":"at how many clinicians it took to take care of you"},{"time":364000,"text":"if you came into a hospital,"},{"time":366000,"text":"as it changed over time."},{"time":368000,"text":"And in the year 1970,"},{"time":370000,"text":"it took just over two full-time equivalents of clinicians."},{"time":373000,"text":"That is to say,"},{"time":375000,"text":"it took basically the nursing time"},{"time":378000,"text":"and then just a little bit of time for a doctor"},{"time":380000,"text":"who more or less checked in on you"},{"time":382000,"text":"once a day."},{"time":384000,"text":"By the end of the 20th century,"},{"time":387000,"text":"it had become more than 15 clinicians"},{"time":390000,"text":"for the same typical hospital patient --"},{"time":393000,"text":"specialists, physical therapists,"},{"time":396000,"text":"the nurses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399000,"text":"We're all specialists now,"},{"time":401000,"text":"even the primary care physicians."},{"time":403000,"text":"Everyone just has"},{"time":405000,"text":"a piece of the care."},{"time":408000,"text":"But holding onto that structure we built"},{"time":410000,"text":"around the daring, independence,"},{"time":412000,"text":"self-sufficiency"},{"time":414000,"text":"of each of those people"},{"time":417000,"text":"has become a disaster."},{"time":419000,"text":"We have trained, hired and rewarded people"},{"time":423000,"text":"to be cowboys."},{"time":426000,"text":"But it's pit crews that we need,"},{"time":429000,"text":"pit crews for patients."}]},{"cues":[{"time":431000,"text":"There's evidence all around us:"},{"time":433000,"text":"40 percent of our coronary artery disease patients"},{"time":436000,"text":"in our communities"},{"time":438000,"text":"receive incomplete or inappropriate care."},{"time":442000,"text":"60 percent"},{"time":444000,"text":"of our asthma, stroke patients"},{"time":447000,"text":"receive incomplete or inappropriate care."},{"time":451000,"text":"Two million people come into hospitals"},{"time":454000,"text":"and pick up an infection"},{"time":456000,"text":"they didn't have"},{"time":458000,"text":"because someone failed to follow"},{"time":461000,"text":"the basic practices of hygiene."},{"time":464000,"text":"Our experience"},{"time":466000,"text":"as people who get sick,"},{"time":468000,"text":"need help from other people,"},{"time":470000,"text":"is that we have amazing clinicians"},{"time":473000,"text":"that we can turn to --"},{"time":475000,"text":"hardworking, incredibly well-trained and very smart --"},{"time":478000,"text":"that we have access to incredible technologies"},{"time":481000,"text":"that give us great hope,"},{"time":483000,"text":"but little sense"},{"time":485000,"text":"that it consistently all comes together for you"},{"time":489000,"text":"from start to finish"},{"time":492000,"text":"in a successful way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495000,"text":"There's another sign"},{"time":497000,"text":"that we need pit crews,"},{"time":499000,"text":"and that's the unmanageable cost"},{"time":502000,"text":"of our care."},{"time":505000,"text":"Now we in medicine, I think,"},{"time":507000,"text":"are baffled by this question of cost."},{"time":509000,"text":"We want to say, \"This is just the way it is."},{"time":513000,"text":"This is just what medicine requires.\""},{"time":515000,"text":"When you go from a world"},{"time":517000,"text":"where you treated arthritis with aspirin,"},{"time":520000,"text":"that mostly didn't do the job,"},{"time":523000,"text":"to one where, if it gets bad enough,"},{"time":525000,"text":"we can do a hip replacement, a knee replacement"},{"time":527000,"text":"that gives you years, maybe decades,"},{"time":530000,"text":"without disability,"},{"time":532000,"text":"a dramatic change,"},{"time":534000,"text":"well is it any surprise"},{"time":536000,"text":"that that $40,000 hip replacement"},{"time":539000,"text":"replacing the 10-cent aspirin"},{"time":541000,"text":"is more expensive?"},{"time":543000,"text":"It's just the way it is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":546000,"text":"But I think we're ignoring certain facts"},{"time":548000,"text":"that tell us something about what we can do."},{"time":553000,"text":"As we've looked at the data"},{"time":555000,"text":"about the results that have come"},{"time":558000,"text":"as the complexity has increased,"},{"time":560000,"text":"we found"},{"time":562000,"text":"that the most expensive care"},{"time":564000,"text":"is not necessarily the best care."},{"time":567000,"text":"And vice versa,"},{"time":569000,"text":"the best care"},{"time":571000,"text":"often turns out to be the least expensive --"},{"time":574000,"text":"has fewer complications,"},{"time":577000,"text":"the people get more efficient at what they do."},{"time":580000,"text":"And what that means"},{"time":582000,"text":"is there's hope."},{"time":585000,"text":"Because [if] to have the best results,"},{"time":588000,"text":"you really needed the most expensive care"},{"time":591000,"text":"in the country, or in the world,"},{"time":593000,"text":"well then we really would be talking about rationing"},{"time":596000,"text":"who we're going to cut off from Medicare."},{"time":600000,"text":"That would be really our only choice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":604000,"text":"But when we look at the positive deviants --"},{"time":606000,"text":"the ones who are getting the best results"},{"time":609000,"text":"at the lowest costs --"},{"time":611000,"text":"we find the ones that look the most like systems"},{"time":614000,"text":"are the most successful."},{"time":616000,"text":"That is to say, they found ways"},{"time":619000,"text":"to get all of the different pieces,"},{"time":621000,"text":"all of the different components,"},{"time":623000,"text":"to come together into a whole."},{"time":626000,"text":"Having great components is not enough,"},{"time":629000,"text":"and yet we've been obsessed in medicine with components."},{"time":633000,"text":"We want the best drugs, the best technologies,"},{"time":636000,"text":"the best specialists,"},{"time":639000,"text":"but we don't think too much"},{"time":641000,"text":"about how it all comes together."},{"time":644000,"text":"It's a terrible design strategy actually."}]},{"cues":[{"time":648000,"text":"There's a famous thought experiment"},{"time":651000,"text":"that touches exactly on this"},{"time":653000,"text":"that said, what if you built a car"},{"time":655000,"text":"from the very best car parts?"},{"time":658000,"text":"Well it would lead you to put in Porsche brakes,"},{"time":661000,"text":"a Ferrari engine,"},{"time":663000,"text":"a Volvo body, a BMW chassis."},{"time":666000,"text":"And you put it all together and what do you get?"},{"time":669000,"text":"A very expensive pile of junk that does not go anywhere."},{"time":673000,"text":"And that is what medicine can feel like sometimes."},{"time":678000,"text":"It's not a system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":681000,"text":"Now a system, however,"},{"time":683000,"text":"when things start to come together,"},{"time":686000,"text":"you realize it has certain skills"},{"time":689000,"text":"for acting and looking that way."},{"time":692000,"text":"Skill number one"},{"time":694000,"text":"is the ability to recognize success"},{"time":696000,"text":"and the ability to recognize failure."},{"time":699000,"text":"When you are a specialist,"},{"time":701000,"text":"you can't see the end result very well."},{"time":704000,"text":"You have to become really interested in data,"},{"time":707000,"text":"unsexy as that sounds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":709000,"text":"One of my colleagues is a surgeon in Cedar Rapids, Iowa,"},{"time":712000,"text":"and he got interested in the question of,"},{"time":716000,"text":"well how many CT scans did they do"},{"time":718000,"text":"for their community in Cedar Rapids?"},{"time":720000,"text":"He got interested in this"},{"time":722000,"text":"because there had been government reports,"},{"time":724000,"text":"newspaper reports, journal articles"},{"time":726000,"text":"saying that there had been too many CT scans done."},{"time":729000,"text":"He didn't see it in his own patients."},{"time":733000,"text":"And so he asked the question, \"How many did we do?\""},{"time":735000,"text":"and he wanted to get the data."},{"time":737000,"text":"It took him three months."},{"time":739000,"text":"No one had asked this question in his community before."},{"time":742000,"text":"And what he found was that,"},{"time":744000,"text":"for the 300,000 people in their community,"},{"time":746000,"text":"in the previous year"},{"time":748000,"text":"they had done 52,000 CT scans."},{"time":753000,"text":"They had found a problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":756000,"text":"Which brings us to skill number two a system has."},{"time":761000,"text":"Skill one, find where your failures are."},{"time":764000,"text":"Skill two is devise solutions."},{"time":768000,"text":"I got interested in this"},{"time":770000,"text":"when the World Health Organization came to my team"},{"time":772000,"text":"asking if we could help with a project"},{"time":774000,"text":"to reduce deaths in surgery."},{"time":776000,"text":"The volume of surgery had spread"},{"time":778000,"text":"around the world,"},{"time":780000,"text":"but the safety of surgery"},{"time":782000,"text":"had not."},{"time":784000,"text":"Now our usual tactics for tackling problems like these"},{"time":787000,"text":"are to do more training,"},{"time":789000,"text":"give people more specialization"},{"time":792000,"text":"or bring in more technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":795000,"text":"Well in surgery, you couldn't have people who are more specialized"},{"time":798000,"text":"and you couldn't have people who are better trained."},{"time":801000,"text":"And yet we see unconscionable levels"},{"time":804000,"text":"of death, disability"},{"time":808000,"text":"that could be avoided."},{"time":810000,"text":"And so we looked at what other high-risk industries do."},{"time":812000,"text":"We looked at skyscraper construction,"},{"time":814000,"text":"we looked at the aviation world,"},{"time":817000,"text":"and we found"},{"time":819000,"text":"that they have technology, they have training,"},{"time":821000,"text":"and then they have one other thing:"},{"time":824000,"text":"They have checklists."},{"time":827000,"text":"I did not expect"},{"time":829000,"text":"to be spending a significant part"},{"time":831000,"text":"of my time as a Harvard surgeon"},{"time":833000,"text":"worrying about checklists."},{"time":836000,"text":"And yet, what we found"},{"time":838000,"text":"were that these were tools"},{"time":841000,"text":"to help make experts better."},{"time":844000,"text":"We got the lead safety engineer for Boeing to help us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":848000,"text":"Could we design a checklist for surgery?"},{"time":851000,"text":"Not for the lowest people on the totem pole,"},{"time":853000,"text":"but for the folks"},{"time":855000,"text":"who were all the way around the chain,"},{"time":857000,"text":"the entire team including the surgeons."},{"time":859000,"text":"And what they taught us"},{"time":861000,"text":"was that designing a checklist"},{"time":863000,"text":"to help people handle complexity"},{"time":865000,"text":"actually involves more difficulty than I had understood."},{"time":868000,"text":"You have to think about things"},{"time":870000,"text":"like pause points."},{"time":872000,"text":"You need to identify the moments in a process"},{"time":875000,"text":"when you can actually catch a problem before it's a danger"},{"time":877000,"text":"and do something about it."},{"time":879000,"text":"You have to identify"},{"time":881000,"text":"that this is a before-takeoff checklist."},{"time":884000,"text":"And then you need to focus on the killer items."},{"time":887000,"text":"An aviation checklist,"},{"time":889000,"text":"like this one for a single-engine plane,"},{"time":891000,"text":"isn't a recipe for how to fly a plane,"},{"time":893000,"text":"it's a reminder of the key things"},{"time":895000,"text":"that get forgotten or missed"},{"time":898000,"text":"if they're not checked."}]},{"cues":[{"time":900000,"text":"So we did this."},{"time":902000,"text":"We created a 19-item two-minute checklist"},{"time":905000,"text":"for surgical teams."},{"time":907000,"text":"We had the pause points"},{"time":909000,"text":"immediately before anesthesia is given,"},{"time":912000,"text":"immediately before the knife hits the skin,"},{"time":915000,"text":"immediately before the patient leaves the room."},{"time":918000,"text":"And we had a mix of dumb stuff on there --"},{"time":921000,"text":"making sure an antibiotic is given in the right time frame"},{"time":924000,"text":"because that cuts the infection rate by half --"},{"time":926000,"text":"and then interesting stuff,"},{"time":928000,"text":"because you can't make a recipe for something as complicated as surgery."},{"time":931000,"text":"Instead, you can make a recipe"},{"time":933000,"text":"for how to have a team that's prepared for the unexpected."},{"time":936000,"text":"And we had items like making sure everyone in the room"},{"time":939000,"text":"had introduced themselves by name at the start of the day,"},{"time":942000,"text":"because you get half a dozen people or more"},{"time":944000,"text":"who are sometimes coming together as a team"},{"time":947000,"text":"for the very first time that day that you're coming in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":950000,"text":"We implemented this checklist"},{"time":952000,"text":"in eight hospitals around the world,"},{"time":955000,"text":"deliberately in places from rural Tanzania"},{"time":957000,"text":"to the University of Washington in Seattle."},{"time":960000,"text":"We found that after they adopted it"},{"time":963000,"text":"the complication rates fell"},{"time":965000,"text":"35 percent."},{"time":967000,"text":"It fell in every hospital it went into."},{"time":970000,"text":"The death rates fell"},{"time":972000,"text":"47 percent."},{"time":975000,"text":"This was bigger than a drug."}]},{"cues":[{"time":977000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":983000,"text":"And that brings us"},{"time":985000,"text":"to skill number three,"},{"time":988000,"text":"the ability to implement this,"},{"time":990000,"text":"to get colleagues across the entire chain"},{"time":993000,"text":"to actually do these things."},{"time":996000,"text":"And it's been slow to spread."},{"time":998000,"text":"This is not yet our norm in surgery --"},{"time":1002000,"text":"let alone making checklists"},{"time":1004000,"text":"to go onto childbirth and other areas."},{"time":1007000,"text":"There's a deep resistance"},{"time":1009000,"text":"because using these tools"},{"time":1011000,"text":"forces us to confront"},{"time":1013000,"text":"that we're not a system,"},{"time":1015000,"text":"forces us to behave with a different set of values."},{"time":1018000,"text":"Just using a checklist"},{"time":1020000,"text":"requires you to embrace different values from the ones we've had,"},{"time":1023000,"text":"like humility,"},{"time":1027000,"text":"discipline,"},{"time":1030000,"text":"teamwork."},{"time":1032000,"text":"This is the opposite of what we were built on:"},{"time":1035000,"text":"independence, self-sufficiency,"},{"time":1037000,"text":"autonomy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1040000,"text":"I met an actual cowboy, by the way."},{"time":1043000,"text":"I asked him, what was it like"},{"time":1046000,"text":"to actually herd a thousand cattle"},{"time":1048000,"text":"across hundreds of miles?"},{"time":1050000,"text":"How did you do that?"},{"time":1052000,"text":"And he said, \"We have the cowboys stationed at distinct places all around.\""},{"time":1055000,"text":"They communicate electronically constantly,"},{"time":1058000,"text":"and they have protocols and checklists"},{"time":1060000,"text":"for how they handle everything --"},{"time":1062000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1064000,"text":"-- from bad weather"},{"time":1066000,"text":"to emergencies or inoculations for the cattle."},{"time":1069000,"text":"Even the cowboys are pit crews now."},{"time":1073000,"text":"And it seemed like time"},{"time":1075000,"text":"that we become that way ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1077000,"text":"Making systems work"},{"time":1079000,"text":"is the great task of my generation"},{"time":1082000,"text":"of physicians and scientists."},{"time":1084000,"text":"But I would go further and say"},{"time":1086000,"text":"that making systems work,"},{"time":1088000,"text":"whether in health care, education,"},{"time":1090000,"text":"climate change,"},{"time":1092000,"text":"making a pathway out of poverty,"},{"time":1094000,"text":"is the great task of our generation as a whole."},{"time":1098000,"text":"In every field, knowledge has exploded,"},{"time":1101000,"text":"but it has brought complexity,"},{"time":1103000,"text":"it has brought specialization."},{"time":1106000,"text":"And we've come to a place where we have no choice"},{"time":1108000,"text":"but to recognize,"},{"time":1110000,"text":"as individualistic as we want to be,"},{"time":1113000,"text":"complexity requires"},{"time":1116000,"text":"group success."},{"time":1118000,"text":"We all need to be pit crews now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1122000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1124000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}